# Knowledge Index

Route to the right knowledge file based on what you need. Updated on each `/hd:maintain capture` + graduation.

## Domains

| Domain | Memory Type | File | Entries | Last Updated | Top Tags |
|--------|-------------|------|---------|--------------|----------|
